import { Box, Button, ButtonGroup, Divider, Stack, TextField, Typography } from '@mui/material';
import Container from '@mui/material/Container';
import { useState } from 'react';
import api from './api'

export default function PeixesCadastrados() {
    const [peixes,setPeixes]=useState([])
    async function baixarDados(){
        const response= await api.get('peixes');
        console.log(response.data);
        setPeixes(response.data);
    }

    return (
        <div>
            
            <Container maxWidth="md">
                <Stack direction='row' spacing={50}   >
                    <Stack direction='column' spacing={2}   >

                        <Typography>Identificador:{console.log({peixes})}</Typography>
                        <Typography>PitTag:</Typography>
                        <Typography>Nome Científico da Espécie:</Typography>
                        <Typography>Local da Captura::</Typography>
                        <Typography>Data da Soltura:</Typography>
                        <Typography>Local da Soltura:</Typography>
                        <Typography>Código de Amostra do DNA:</Typography>
                        <Typography>Recaptura:</Typography>
                    </Stack>

                    <Stack direction='column' spacing={25}   >
                        <TextField

                            label="Digite para buscar um peixe"
                            variant='outlined'
                            color='primary'
                            required

                        />
                        <Box>
                            <ButtonGroup size="small" aria-label=" small button group" variant='text' color="inherit">
                                <Button  >Recaptura</Button>
                                <Button>Editar</Button>
                                <Button>Excluir</Button>
                            </ButtonGroup>

                        </Box>
                    </Stack>

                </Stack>
               

            </Container >


        </div >

    )
}
